without actually winning.

1151
01:18:28.007 --> 01:18:29.617
Is that what's happening to you?

1152
01:18:31.532 --> 01:18:34.709
I see you still don't
understand how this sport works.

1153
01:18:34.796 --> 01:18:38.669
