lose against yourself.

1156
01:18:43.239 --> 01:18:45.328
Is that how you feel right now?

1157
01:18:45.502 --> 01:18:46.808
What do you mean?

1158
01:18:46.895 --> 01:18:48.941
Like someone
who's going to withdraw

1159
01:18:49.028 --> 01:18:51.334
because he's lost
against himself.

