1244
01:24:28.715 --> 01:24:31.457
Mine? My job is to win.

1245
01:24:33.633 --> 01:24:35.983
Why is it so important?

1246
01:24:36.070 --> 01:24:38.594
I've been with you guys
for a while now and I,

1247
01:24:38.681 --> 01:24:40.944
