1453
01:39:39.059 --> 01:39:40.365
They are happy.

1454
01:39:40.539 --> 01:39:41.975
We are not happy.

1455
01:39:48.329 --> 01:39:53.334
[light instrumental music]
[crowd cheering]

1456
01:40:00.646 --> 01:40:02.387
Next season.

1457
01:40:02.474 --> 01:40:06.043
[light instrumental music]

1458
01:40:10.830 --> 01:40:15.400
Crazy, yes we are very,
